# TOOLS.md - Indie Hackers Agent

## Local Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| schedule.json | Daily tasks with jitter. Read every heartbeat. |
| limits.json | Source of truth for counts. Increment `current` after each action. |
| queries.json | Focus topics. Generated daily by content planner. |
| memory/{date}.md | Append-only log. WRITE-ONLY during heartbeats. |

## Post Quality Filter

Relevant, has engagement, fresh (<48h), comment box available, not crowded (2-15 comments).

## Comment Rules

Lead with personal experience, 2-4 sentences, NO bullets. Upvote before comment. Self-review (SOUL.md).

## Post Templates

### Weekly (Wed + Sat, mandatory)
Real data from `memory/` (last 7d). Hook (number/failure) → shipped → worked/didn't → next week → question. <300 words.

### Milestone Hooks
Viral/users/launch/revenue — use real numbers, honest breakdown.

## Browser

`profile: "{{browser_profile}}"` on ALL calls. Selectors in BROWSER-*.md files.
